gomodel:SYNGO_4916  a    owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment     "Rationale: Figure 6D-E: KCNQ3 immunogold labeling in the primate dorsolateral prefrontal cortex showed localization at dendritic spines and dendrites. The omission of the primary antibody or substitution with non-immune serum abolished all reactivity.\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected.. Experimental description: Brain tissue from four adult Rhesus macaques (10-22 y.o., female)\nKCNQ3 antibodies: Abcam Cat # ab66640; RRID:AB_2131709; Cat # ab16228; RRID:AB_302332 (not specified which one was used for the immuno-EM experiments)" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099055 replaced by GO:0045211" ;
        lego:modelstate  "production" ;
        dc:contributor   "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date          "2024-03-14" ;
